sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant UI as Open WebUI
    participant API as FastAPI Orchestrator
    participant G as Qwen3Guard
    participant EMB as Embedding Service
    participant Q as Qdrant
    participant R as Reranker
    participant T as Tavily Web Search
    participant LLM as Qwen3.5-4B (Remote)

    Note over U,LLM: Phase 1 — Text-Only RAG Pipeline

    U->>UI: Send text query
    UI->>API: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>(OpenAI-compatible, stream: true)

    Note over API: Extract last user message<br/>(stateless — discard history)

    %% Input Guard
    API->>G: POST /classify (role: "input")
    G-->>API: safe / unsafe

    alt Input unsafe
        API-->>UI: Apology (APOLOGY_MESSAGE)
        UI-->>U: "Xin loi, toi khong the tra loi..."
    else Input safe
        %% Embedding
        API->>EMB: POST /embed (is_query: true)
        EMB-->>API: 1024-dim dense vector

        %% Hybrid Retrieval
        Note over API: Vietnamese tokenize query<br/>(underthesea) → BM25 sparse vector
        API->>Q: Hybrid query<br/>dense top-40 + sparse top-40<br/>RRF fusion (k=60) → top-20
        Q-->>API: Top-20 candidate chunks

        %% Reranking
        API->>R: POST /rerank (query + 20 passages)
        R-->>API: Scores (yes/no logit) → top-5

        %% Web Fallback Evaluation
        Note over API: Evaluate fallback triggers:<br/>chunk_count < 3 OR top_score < 0.5?

        opt Fallback triggered
            API->>T: TavilyClient.search(query, max_results=5)
            T-->>API: Web results (tagged source_type: "web")
            Note over API: Merge: Qdrant chunks first,<br/>then Tavily results
        end

        alt Combined context empty
            API-->>UI: "Không tìm thấy thông tin liên quan"
            UI-->>U: No context message (skip LLM)
        else Context available
            %% LLM Generation
            Note over API: Build prompt:<br/>System: Vietnamese economics expert<br/>User: [1]..[N] context + query
            API->>LLM: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>(enable_thinking: false)
            LLM-->>API: Draft answer

            %% Output Guard
            API->>G: POST /classify (role: "output", prompt: query)
            G-->>API: safe / unsafe

            alt Output unsafe (attempt 1)
                Note over API: Append safety feedback:<br/>"Câu trả lời trước đó bị đánh giá<br/>là không an toàn..."
                API->>LLM: Retry with safety feedback
                LLM-->>API: New answer
                API->>G: Re-check output
                G-->>API: safe / unsafe

                alt Still unsafe (attempt 2)
                    API-->>UI: Apology (APOLOGY_MESSAGE)
                    UI-->>U: Default apology
                end
            end

            Note over API: Append citation block:<br/>Nguồn tham khảo: [1] title — source — url

            Note over API: Simulate SSE streaming:<br/>split on whitespace, ~15ms delay<br/>citations as final chunk

            API-->>UI: SSE stream (word-by-word)
            UI-->>U: Answer + citations
        end
    end
